        <!-- Design Principles -->
        <mxCell id="dp_title" value="&lt;b&gt;Design Principles&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=left;fontSize=16;fontColor=#333333;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="840" y="80" width="400" height="30" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dp1" value="1. PhoenixExpert is mandatory before any Phoenix task (Rule 0.4/8)&lt;br&gt;2. Environment must be explicit — never inferred (Rule CONF.0 / DB.0a)&lt;br&gt;3. Phoenix code is NEVER edited — read-only via aligned branches (Rule 0.8)&lt;br&gt;4. EnergoTS tests/ writable ONLY by EnergoTSTestAgent (Rule 0.8.1)&lt;br&gt;5. Confluence + GitLab = read-only always (Rule 1)&lt;br&gt;6. Swagger refresh mandatory before .spec.ts files (Rule 41)&lt;br&gt;7. No beforeAll in EnergoTS preconditions (Rule 40)&lt;br&gt;8. Every response: Confidence % + Agents involved (Rules CONF.1 / 0.1)&lt;br&gt;9. Disk reports only on /report, /feedback, HandsOff — NOT by default (Rule 0.6)&lt;br&gt;10. Jira bugs: Experiments board only, never Phoenix delivery (Rule JIRA.0)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#333333;fontSize=12;align=left;spacingLeft=10;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="840" y="120" width="600" height="240" as="geometry"/>
        </mxCell>

